data.description: Well maintained home in Waiakea Heights ready for a new owner.  Situated on high lot on the mauka side of the street, this home faces and enjoys tradewinds from the oceanside.  A large swinging bench greets guests as they enter the foyer.  The fenced and gated grassy yard with rock walls, is private and encompases the back half of the lot.  Inside, tile floors and high vaulted ceilings help keep the home cool.  The kitchen with lots of counter space, features two sinks and an island bar.  In addition, there's a movable matching table for added storage and seating.  Corresponding matching bookshelf built-ins are located in the den or seperate space for use as an office.   Bedrooms feature laminate flooring and window AC units.  Both bathrooms feature tub and shower combo with new shower heads.   The garage is deep and spacious with additional cabinet storage/workshop space.  Just off the garage into the house, is an interior laundry room adjacent to a pantry for additional storage space.
